text: Heinz Weigel (born 11 April 1938) is a West German rower who represented the United Team of Germany. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics in Rome with the men's coxless pair where they came fourth. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:People from Halberstadt Category:People from the Province of Saxony Category:West German male rowers Category:Sportspeople from Saxony-Anhalt Category:Olympic rowers of the United Team of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1960 Summer Olympics
